# PDF Storage Directory

This directory stores appointment confirmation PDFs organized by year-month subdirectories.

## Directory Structure

```
pdfs/
├── 2026-03/
│   ├── confirmation_abc123_1711098765432.pdf
│   └── confirmation_def456_1711098765433.pdf
├── 2026-04/
│   └── ...
└── .gitkeep (this file)
```

## Naming Convention

Files follow the format: `confirmation_[appointment_id]_[timestamp].pdf`

- **appointment_id**: UUID of the appointment
- **timestamp**: Unix timestamp in milliseconds when PDF was generated

## Retention Policy

- PDFs are automatically deleted after 30 days from generation date
- Cleanup job runs daily at 2 AM UTC
- Patients can regenerate PDFs from appointment history if needed

## Security

- Direct filesystem access is restricted
- Access is only via secure download URLs with JWT tokens
- Download URLs expire after 7 days

## Storage Management

- Subdirectories organized by year-month to avoid filesystem limits
- Each subdirectory can handle ~10,000 files efficiently
- Total storage monitored via pdf_metadata table
